<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٣٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عبد اللَّه ابن الشخير [عن أخيه مطرف <span class="c2">(بن)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> عبد اللَّه بن الشخير] <span class="c2">(٣)</span> قال: إن اللَّه <span class="c2">(يرحم)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> <span class="c2">(برحمة)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span> العصفور.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
